data.title: Ukraine Cities Database
data.meta_description: A database of 221 prominent cities in Ukraine.  Includes a city's latitude, longitude, province and other variables of interest. MIT license.  CSV, Excel and JSON formats. Comprehensive database available.
data.text:
Below is a list of 221 prominent cities in Ukraine. Each row includes a city's latitude, longitude, province and other variables of interest. This is a subset of all 32,498 places in Ukraine (and only some of the fields) that you'll find in our World Cities Database. We're releasing this data subset for free under an MIT license. You're free to use the data below for personal or commercial applications. The data below can be downloaded in .csv, .json, and .xlsx formats.

Notable Cities: The capital of Ukraine is Kyiv, which is in the city of Kyiv, Misto. The largest city in Ukraine is Kyiv, with an urban population of 2,952,301.
